Class ConsensusSpectrumReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • dia.ConsensusSpectrumReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<org.Spectrums.Spectrum>

    public class ConsensusSpectrumReader
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<org.Spectrums.Spectrum>
    This class read in multiple consecutive SWATH spectra in retention time and analyze them together so consensus information among multiple spectra can be utilized to analyze DIA data
    Author:
    Jian
